#. HTML: <section id="vagga"><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.21" id="21"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an1.21-30:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 1 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 1 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: akammanīyavagga (pts1)
msgctxt "an1.21-30:0.2"
msgid "3. Akammaniyavagga "
msgstr "3. Useless "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an1.21-30:0.3"
msgid "21 "
msgstr "21 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc21.1
#. VAR: yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ → yathayidaṃ cittaṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an1.21-30:21.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ abhāvitaṃ akammaniyaṃ hoti yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it’s not developed like this, is as useless as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.21-30:21.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, abhāvitaṃ akammaniyaṃ hotī”ti. "
msgstr "An undeveloped mind is useless.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.21-30:21.1.3"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.22" id="22"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.21-30:21.1.4"
msgid "22 "
msgstr "22 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc22.1
msgctxt "an1.21-30:22.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ bhāvitaṃ kammaniyaṃ hoti yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is developed like this, is as workable as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.21-30:22.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvitaṃ kammaniyaṃ hotī”ti. "
msgstr "A developed mind is workable.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.21-30:22.1.3"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.23" id="23"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.21-30:22.1.4"
msgid "23 "
msgstr "23 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc23.1
msgctxt "an1.21-30:23.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ abhāvitaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it’s not developed like this, is so very harmful as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.21-30:23.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, abhāvitaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "An undeveloped mind is very harmful.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.21-30:23.1.3"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.24" id="24"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.21-30:23.1.4"
msgid "24 "
msgstr "24 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc24.1
msgctxt "an1.21-30:24.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ bhāvitaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is developed like this, is so very beneficial as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.21-30:24.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvitaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "A developed mind is very beneficial.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.21-30:24.1.3"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.25" id="25"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.21-30:24.1.4"
msgid "25 "
msgstr "25 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc25.1
msgctxt "an1.21-30:25.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ abhāvitaṃ apātubhūtaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it’s not developed, with such untapped potential, is so very harmful as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.21-30:25.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, abhāvitaṃ apātubhūtaṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "An undeveloped mind, with untapped potential, is very harmful.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.21-30:25.1.3"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.26" id="26"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.21-30:25.1.4"
msgid "26 "
msgstr "26 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.6, sc26.1
msgctxt "an1.21-30:26.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ bhāvitaṃ pātubhūtaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is developed, with its potential realized, is so very beneficial as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.21-30:26.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvitaṃ pātubhūtaṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "A developed mind, with its potential realized, is very beneficial.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.21-30:26.1.3"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.27" id="27"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.21-30:26.1.4"
msgid "27 "
msgstr "27 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc27.1
msgctxt "an1.21-30:27.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ abhāvitaṃ abahulīkataṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it’s not developed and cultivated, is so very harmful as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.21-30:27.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, abhāvitaṃ abahulīkataṃ mahato anatthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "An undeveloped and uncultivated mind is very harmful.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.21-30:27.1.3"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.28" id="28"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.21-30:27.1.4"
msgid "28 "
msgstr "28 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc28.1
msgctxt "an1.21-30:28.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is developed and cultivated, is so very beneficial as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.21-30:28.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ mahato atthāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "A developed and cultivated mind is very beneficial.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.21-30:28.1.3"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.29" id="29"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.21-30:28.1.4"
msgid "29 "
msgstr "29 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc29.1
msgctxt "an1.21-30:29.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ abhāvitaṃ abahulīkataṃ dukkhādhivahaṃ hoti yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it’s not developed and cultivated, brings such suffering as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.21-30:29.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, abhāvitaṃ abahulīkataṃ dukkhādhivahaṃ hotī”ti. "
msgstr "An undeveloped and uncultivated mind brings suffering.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.21-30:29.1.3"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.30" id="30"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.21-30:29.1.4"
msgid "30 "
msgstr "30 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc30.1
msgctxt "an1.21-30:30.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yaṃ evaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ sukhādhivahaṃ hoti yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that, when it is developed and cultivated, brings such happiness as the mind. "

msgctxt "an1.21-30:30.1.2"
msgid "Cittaṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ sukhādhivahaṃ hotī”ti. "
msgstr "A developed and cultivated mind brings happiness.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.21-30:30.1.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.21-30:30.1.4"
msgid "Akammaniyavaggo tatiyo. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></section></body></html>
